00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:21.680
and troubled Melanie Cole converge at the&nbsp;
intriguing Fantasy Island, a tropical resort where&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:27.520
imaginations appear to come true, after winning&nbsp;
a sweepstakes. Mr. Roarke, the island's landlord,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:27.520 --> 00:00:31.840
informs the visitors that they will each be&nbsp;
granted one dream and takes them to their wishes:&nbsp;&nbsp;

