J. D. and Brax are distinguished guests at&nbsp;
a mansion rave, Patrick gets enrolled in the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:36.080 --> 00:00:40.960
military in honour of his late father, Melanie&nbsp;
seeks vengeance on a childhood bully, and Gwen&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:45.440
accepts her ex-boyfriend Allen Chambers' marriage&nbsp;
proposal, which she had previously refused.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:50.640
Melanie finds that her bully, Sloane Maddison,&nbsp;
was abducted and transported to the island to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:50.640 --> 00:00:54.480
execute the fantasy against her will while&nbsp;
tormenting her by releasing an internet&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:54.480 --> 00:00:59.440
video of her cheating on her husband. They flee&nbsp;
